---
title: Loaded Smokey Chicken Flatbreads with Avocado Salsa & Corn Cobs
description: Turn up the heat with these flavour-packed wraps! Juicy chicken meets melted Cheddar on a toasty flatbread, topped off with creamy avocado salsa for a zesty twist. On the side, vibrant corn cobs make it a feast you won’t want to share. Smokey, cheesy, and oh-so-satisfying—dinner just got a serious upgrade!
